297
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:27,920
I was an engineer before.

298
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,760
And later,

299
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:32,440
well, to tell you the truth,

300
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:35,160
you'd have to ask me what I was doing in a specific year and month.

301
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:37,160
Because I've worked in

302
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,440
more than 20 different industries.

303
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,160
Do we even have that many industries in our country?

304
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:43,480
I've been involved in some overseas projects too.

305
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:46,210
Yes, my uncle has lived abroad for over ten years.

306
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,960
No wonder your style

307
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,420
looks quite distinctive.

308
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:51,400
Alright then.

309
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,400
Let's get down to business.

310
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,600
Are you looking to acquire his website?

311
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,760
Rather than acquiring his website,

312
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:58,480
I'd say

313
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:01,320
I'm interested in buying your copyright.

314
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:03,000
You see, I'm not really interested in his website.

315
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
I'm mainly interested in your work.

316
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:08,040
The main reason I came today was to meet you,

317
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,960
to see if there's a chance to sign you directly,

318
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,890
to make you our contracted author.

319
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,240
I... no signing,

320
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,800
no contracts. I'm not a professional writer.

321
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:16,800
I only write because he forces me to.

322
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:22,930
Let's get down to business.

323
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,760
How much are you willing to pay for his website?

324
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:31,360
If Teacher Gu completes the serialization of his work,

325
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,240
I can offer up to 300,000.

326
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,360
No, no.

327
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,480
Miss Zhou,

328
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,080
we've done the calculations.

329
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,760
From the founding of this website until now,

330
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,720
we've invested nearly

331
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:45,800
1.3 million.

332
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:46,880
The logic of capital

333
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,960
is never about how much you invest,

334
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,920
but how much you're worth.

335
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:53,520
If Mr. Gu completes the serialization of his work,

336
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,920
I can offer up to 300,000.

337
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,680
But if you think it's not suitable,

338
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:58,160
then we'll stay in touch.

339
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,720
If one day your website improves,

340
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,980
you can come back to me.

341
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,340
Does that work for you?

342
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,400
Or would you rather look elsewhere?

343
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:05,440
Okay, okay.

344
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:06,400
Good.

345
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:07,200
Just 300,000.

346
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:10,360
Then my conditions must be met.

347
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:13,780
Mr. Gu must complete the serialization of his work.

348
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:15,400
Important things need to be said three times.

349
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,680
This is already the third time I'm saying it.

350
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:19,080
That's no problem at all.

351
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:21,440
Wait a moment.

352
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:23,480
Before you agree to her request,

353
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:26,280
