360
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,120
Will you do it?

361
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,280
I mean,

362
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,170
is that okay?

363
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:44,380
Just tell me if you'll do it or not.

364
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:48,040
Yes, I will.

365
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:49,360
Then I have no issues.

366
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:52,160
Have you really not considered becoming a professional writer?

367
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,220
No, I can't do that.

368
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,720
Being forced to write

369
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,600
is painful enough already.

370
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:57,280
If I had a contract binding me as well,

371
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:59,410
I probably wouldn't live much longer.

372
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:00,900
I respect that.

373
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,500
Make sure you keep your promise to me.

374
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,400
Thank you. Thank you.

375
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,760
That's enough now.

376
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,000
Let me drive you to the airport.

377
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,560
No need,

378
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:12,160
we can take a taxi ourselves.

379
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,320
I'm going to the mountains to feed my dogs. It's on the way.

380
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,320
Then I won't refuse.

381
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:15,850
Let's go.

382
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:24,880
Miss Zhou.

