391
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,280
The car you drive doesn't matter.

392
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:47,120
Being happy is what matters.

393
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,440
You mentioned earlier that you've worked in

394
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,040
