402
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,839
In those nightclubs,

403
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:14,319
Cantonese songs were all the rage.

404
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:17,319
I sing Cantonese songs at nightclubs.

405
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:21,640
Could you sing a bit for us?

406
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,200
Sure.

407
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:17,600
Fragrant but expensive.

408
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,400
I'm up in the mountains.

409
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,880
I'll write it when I get home.

410
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,760
That's not what I'm calling about.

411
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:28,360
I just called Grandpa.

412
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,360
He didn't answer.

413
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,280
I'm busy right now.

414
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,880
Why don't you go check on him?

415
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,730
Alright, I understand.

416
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:49,800
Dad.

