424
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:10,520
You scared me sleeping like that.

425
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:12,250
Why are you lying on this thing?

426
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:14,000
I don't know either.

427
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:16,880
