434
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,000
No need.

435
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,120
How are you feeling?

436
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,760
I feel like

437
00:19:55,560 --> 00:19:58,240
my time might be coming to an end.

438
00:19:59,600 --> 00:20:02,560
Seventy-three to eighty-four is a critical time.

439
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:07,600
I'm afraid I won't make it past this hurdle.

440
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:08,920
Stop talking nonsense.

441
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,850
What hurdle are you talking about?

442
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,680
I know my own body.

443
00:20:15,840 --> 00:20:17,400
At my age,

444
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:24,000
being able to die in my own bed

445
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:25,860
would be a good ending.

446
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:30,760
My grandchildren are all grown up,

447
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:34,010
my granddaughter is almost getting married.

448
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:36,920
I have no regrets.

449
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:41,100
That's enough, Dad. Stop talking, you're wasting energy.

450
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:45,080
I want to say a few words.

451
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,890
Are you still trying to control me?

452
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,130
Go ahead, speak.

453
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:52,480
If I have any regrets,

454
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:55,120
