455
00:20:57,800 --> 00:21:01,320
Old Master Zhang instructed me before he died

456
00:21:02,160 --> 00:21:06,720
to keep Dingqing Restaurant running for a hundred years.

457
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:11,160
To pass down this culinary craft.

458
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:14,760
But now,

459
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,820
Dingqing Restaurant is gone,

460
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:21,640
and no one in our family is in this profession.

461
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:26,800
