465
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:41,200
Half for Old Master Zhang,

466
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:43,720
and half for me.

467
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,170
When I'm in the underworld,

468
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:51,160
I'll apologize to Old Master Zhang.

469
00:22:02,080 --> 00:22:02,640
This one,

470
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:05,400
keep it safe.

471
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,160
Just in case

472
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:11,040
someone in our family

473
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:13,490
wants to become a chef someday,

474
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,040
give it to them.

475
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:18,680
In this society,

476
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,520
no matter when,

477
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,640
we'll always need chefs.

478
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:25,640
