498
00:23:58,520 --> 00:23:59,080
Really?

499
00:23:59,520 --> 00:24:00,520
Trust me.

500
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:01,760
I'll give it a try.

501
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:05,400
