502
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,440
I quit my job to come back.

503
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:10,440
I'll stay for a while.

504
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,200
That's great.

505
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:14,440
Spend more time with Dad.

506
00:24:22,120 --> 00:24:24,120
Which district is this?

507
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:25,450
It's so well developed.

508
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,650
Longshan District.

509
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:30,740
It's even better than abroad.

510
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:32,560
That's why I keep saying China is so good now.

511
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:33,720
Why do you have to

512
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,160
