00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,320
Didn't you order dumplings?

575
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,440
I know.

576
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:14,460
I also know your name is Huo Dongfeng.

577
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,500
Do you want garlic?

578
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,730
I can peel it for you.

579
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,200
What's up?

580
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:47,400
Hey girl,

581
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,960
are you Cui Xiaohong?

582
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,120
Wait there,

583
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:51,580
I'll come down to find you.

584
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:58,280
Gentlemen,

585
00:31:58,280 --> 00:31:59,040
please tell me if you need anything.

586
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,500
This doesn't concern you.

587
00:32:02,080 --> 00:32:03,120
Shut up.

588
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,800
What a surprise,

589
00:32:11,840 --> 00:32:13,100
running into you here.

590
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:15,440
You're quite famous.

591
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,680
Famous for what?

592
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:19,240
Beautiful, pretty, and attractive.

593
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,400
Like I need you to tell me.

594
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,400
I got two movie tickets today.

595
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:27,400
Look, the movie's starting.

596
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,840
We still have half an hour.

597
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:30,440
Come watch the movie with me.

598
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:34,280
Three people, two tickets.

599
00:32:35,040 --> 00:32:36,160
How are we supposed to watch?

600
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,090
Here's the deal,

601
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,240
choose one of us.

602
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,420
I can't choose.

603
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:43,160
Why can't you choose?

604
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:46,160
I'm not interested in either of you.

605
00:32:46,760 --> 00:32:48,120
What are you laughing at?

606
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,280
Eat your dumplings.

607
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:53,840
Think carefully about your choice.

608
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:55,500
I'm quite handsome, you know.

609
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:57,280
Have you finished peeling?

610
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:58,000
Yes.

611
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,880
What exactly are you trying to do?

612
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:10,840
You think this store

613
00:33:10,840 --> 00:33:11,700
belongs to you?

614
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:13,760
It's my family's business.

615
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:15,690
My dad is the general manager here.

616
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,120
Stop talking about managers and all that nonsense.

617
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:19,120
I asked you to watch a movie with me

618
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:20,800
and now you're finding problems with it?

619
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:21,480
I'm going to choose today.

620
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:22,880
I've decided on this one.

621
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,700
What are you doing?

622
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,410
I just want to watch a movie.

623
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:29,280
What are you doing?

624
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,040
Let go.

625
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:33,900
What are you doing?

626
00:33:36,320 --> 00:33:37,320
Someone come quickly!

627
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:38,040
Zhang!

628
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,160
Help!

629
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,360
Someone help!

630
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,480
I'll kill you!

631
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,240
Help! Somebody!

632
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,440
Murder!

633
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:04,520
Stop! Don't run!

634
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:07,720
Call for help!

635
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:09,480
Call for help now!

636
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,090
My name is Cui Xiaohong.

637
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:51,460
Where's your brother?

638
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:52,760
My brother?

639
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:55,320
I thought you were inviting me to a movie.

640
00:35:55,320 --> 00:35:56,850
He's starting school soon.

641
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,760
Let him study instead.

642
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:02,520
Let's go.

643
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:05,000
So all the theaters around here

644
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,360
are accessible to you?

645
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,280
Don't you believe it?

646
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,520
What's wrong, bro?

647
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,050
That happened too quickly.

648
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,440
Where is he?

649
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:31,360
It's nothing.

650
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:32,840
It's fine.

651
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,490
How much did you make today?

652
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:37,600
This.

653
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,290
A little over 20.

654
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:39,930
Here.

655
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,400
All the money you earned today is yours.

656
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,860
Buy some food for the guys.

657
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,090
Thanks, bro.

658
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,160
Go on.

659
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:46,560
Go.

660
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:51,850
Brother,

661
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,020
what happened?

662
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,840
Perfect timing.

663
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:58,370
I brought you the money for the movie tickets.

664
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:59,840
Keep it for yourself.

665
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:02,480
Buy some cigarettes and drinks for the guys.

666
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:03,210
If you say so.

667
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:04,320
Here.

668
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,530
Brother, I was reading a book recently

669
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:11,810
called 'Beacon Fire Mocks the Lords.'

670
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,680
So you're

671
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,700
just messing with us, aren't you?

672
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,840
Had enough?

673
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,860
Stop wasting time.

674
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:20,600
Get to work.

675
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:21,360
Alright,

676
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,280
let's go.

677
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,840
Selling movie tickets?

678
00:37:32,600 --> 00:37:34,240
Sometimes I charge five cents extra.

679
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,770
Sometimes ten cents extra.

680
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,920
Profiteering! Troublemaker!

681
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:41,020
Are you going to arrest me?

682
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:44,560
Well, you're not wrong if you put it that way.

683
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,890
But I can guarantee you.

684
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,760
People who come to these theaters

685
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,840
won't lose their money.

686
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,240
Thieves are afraid of me.

687
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:52,400
I'll beat any one of them.

688
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,570
I'll beat a whole gang if they come.

689
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:56,760
Then why am I not afraid of you?

690
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,760
It's just that when I come here to watch movies in the future,

691
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:06,480
I'll have face being with you.

692
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:10,100
That goes without saying.

693
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:11,800
What are we watching?

694
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,240
Shaolin Temple.

695
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:16,960
Why don't I just look at you instead?

696
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:57,160
Guoming,

697
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:59,000
call your dad's workplace when you get to school.

698
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,130
Okay. Pass the ball!

699
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:02,800
Why call?

700
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,000
Afraid I'll get lost?

701
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,160
You're the one who gets lost.

702
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:07,520
These past few days you told Mom and Dad

703
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:09,000
you were staying at a classmate's house.

704
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:09,840
Where were you really staying?

705
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,100
You think I don't know?

706
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:15,290
Where was I staying?

707
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:17,520
I think Huo Dongfeng

708
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:18,650
is a pretty good guy.

709
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:20,320
I admire him too.

710
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,160
But his looks,

711
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:24,560
he doesn't look like someone from our Cui family.

712
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:25,600
What do you know?

713
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:26,120
I don't know,

714
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,320
those people who hang out in the streets,

715
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,040
whether he is one of them.

716
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,440
He looks like...

717
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:30,960
When he's with you,

718
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,890
he looks like your uncle, you know?

719
00:39:33,040 --> 00:39:33,960
That's not important.

720
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:36,280
What matters is he's always fighting with people.

721
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,600
If he's not fighting,

722
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:38,800
he's on his way to a fight.

723
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,880
Living for today with no thought of tomorrow.

724
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,240
You can admire him,

725
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:43,960
that's fine, but living with him?

726
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,690
Mom and Dad would be terrified.

727
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:46,800
Are you scared?

728
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:47,840
What would I be scared of?

729
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:49,320
I'm not the one dating him.

730
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,840
Then that settles it.

731
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,360
Think about it some more.

732
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:56,000
I've already decided. It's him.

733
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,130
As long as you're happy.

734
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:03,170
Thanks for your effort.

735
00:40:04,520 --> 00:40:05,400
I think

736
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,690
