737
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:14,920
Huo Dongfeng

738
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,260
You don't want us to live anymore, do you?

739
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,200
If you say I don't want you to live,

740
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:24,800
then I don't want you to live.

741
00:40:25,640 --> 00:40:26,360
Others may fear you,

742
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:27,800
but I, Xiasi, don't fear you.

743
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:28,720
Get him!

744
00:41:02,640 --> 00:41:04,500
What are you doing, Huo Dongfeng?

745
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,640
I don't feel well.

746
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:15,050
How much longer do we have to hide here?

747
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:19,530
We need to wait until things cool down.

748
00:41:19,600 --> 00:41:20,920
